      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just got this really intense headache out of nowhere. like, the worst one i've ever had. and i noticed when i look in the mirror that the left side of my face looks a bit heavy/droopy? i get migraines sometimes so i'm thinking it might just be a really bad one or a complex migraine. what do u think?",
